reviews.review_buyer_description: Brown eyes, brown hair, lightMedium skin tone, Combination skin
reviews.review_text: Pigments on this pallet are great and love the shade range. The downside was that the shimmers in the palette irritated my eyes and eyelids so badly. They left my eyes puffy, red, and flaky.

reviews.review_buyer_description: Brown eyes, blonde hair, Light skin tone, Dry skin
reviews.review_text: The palette was ok. It definitely wasn't as pigmented as some of the other pallets.

reviews.review_buyer_description: Blue eyes, brown hair, lightMedium skin tone, Dry skin
reviews.review_text: This palette is perfect. The only downside is that it doesn't have a mirror but that's easy enough to mitigate.  The shadows have high colour payoff  and the shimmers stay in places. I love that the range of shadows offer anything from an everyday look to a more dramatic effect. This is my new fave even outranking my high end palettes.

reviews.review_buyer_description: Blue eyes, red hair, Light skin tone, Dry skin
reviews.review_text: Not a huge fan of Morphe usually but I really liked the look of this palette. I decided to purchase and I used it for the first time the other night and I was really impressed. The colors blended really well and the color payoff is amazing especially the shimmer colors. The lasting power was also super impressive. Highly recommend.
